{{Otheruses|subject=“天安门自焚事件”|other=历史上的其他“天安门事件”|天安门事件}}
{{Infobox event
| title                    = 天安门自焚事件
| image                    =File:天安门自焚.jpg
| caption                  =CCTV画面
| date                     = {{start date|2001|01|23}}
| location                 ={{PRC}}[[北京|北京]][[天安门广场|天安门广场]]
| first_reporter           =[[新华社|新华社]]
}}

'''天安門自焚事件'''，是指發生於2001年1月23日[[除夕|除夕]]當天5人在[[北京|北京]]市中心的[[天安門廣場|天安門廣場]]進行[[自焚|自焚]]行為。[[新華社|新華社]]于事发当日通报称五名[[法輪功|法輪功]]學員在天安門廣場自焚<ref name="xinhua1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.china.org.cn/english/7474.htm|title=The Tragedy of Falun Gong Practitioners|accessdate=2013-02-24|date=2001-01-23|publisher=[[中国网|中国网]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006203446/http://www.china.org.cn/english/7474.htm|archivedate=2012-10-06|quote=|deadurl=no}}</ref>。但是法輪功方面拒绝为这起事件负责，表示在法輪功書籍中明確禁止暴力行為與自殺<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Page|coauthors=Jeremy|title=Survivors say China Falungong inmmolations real|journal=Reuters|date=2002-04-04}}</ref><ref name="violence">{{cite book|title=法轮大法 2003年元宵节讲法|author=李洪志|publisher= 益群书店|language=zh|year=2003|page=P.122|isbn= 978-957-552-723-5}}</ref>。[[法輪功|法輪功]]方面認為整起事件為[[中共|中共]]当局自導自演，為的是引起群眾對法輪功的負面印象，以確立[[打壓法輪功|打壓法輪功]]的合理性<ref name="FDI_PressRelease">{{Cite web|url=http://en.minghui.org/eng/2001/jan/23/vsf012301_3.html|title=PRESS STATEMENT|date=2001-01-31|author=Falun Dafa Information Center|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015055709/http://en.minghui.org/eng/2001/jan/23/vsf012301_3.html|archivedate=2014-10-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://faluninfo.net/article/1114/?cid=84 |title=On Ten Year Anniversary, Tiananmen Square Self-Immolation Continues to Be Deadly Frame-up |publisher=Falun Dafa Information Center |date=2001-01-23 |language=en |accessdate=2013-02-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121127041155/http://faluninfo.net/article/1114/?cid=84 |archivedate=2012-11-27 }}</ref>。

西方媒體與觀察家，質疑共產黨當局及媒體過程中的異常反應、嚴密封鎖，而《華盛頓郵報》等媒體調查後，對於自焚者身份是否為法輪功學員，也與黨媒持不同看法。國際教育發展組織發表聲明認為，此自焚事件是被中共執政當局策劃導演的<ref name="IED" />。

2001年1月31日，[[新華社|新華社]]又改称七人到天安門是為了自焚，其台对该事件的首次報道中，播出了對劉思影的採訪片段，她表示相信自焚將能夠讓她前往天堂。

事发两週後，[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]記者[[菲力普·潘|菲力普·潘]]在一篇名為《Human Fire Ignites Chinese Mystery》的報道中，訪問劉春玲故鄉[[開封市|開封市]]的當地居民有關劉春玲的身份時，獲得以下回應：「在夜總會上班，曾毆打其養母和女兒，沒有人見過她煉法輪功。」<ref name="Pan">{{cite news|url=http://washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/2001/02/04/human-fire-ignites-chinese-mystery/e27303e3-6117-4ec3-b6cf-58f03cdb4773/|author=Philip P. Pan|title=Human Fire Ignites Chinese Mystery|newspaper=Washington Post|language=en|date=2001-02-04|accessdate=2013-02-24|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112123128/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/2001/02/04/human-fire-ignites-chinese-mystery/e27303e3-6117-4ec3-b6cf-58f03cdb4773/}}</ref><ref name="Apple123"/>

[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]組織表示，這起事件對北京當地的採訪記者來說相當艱難，因為所有的資訊皆被封鎖。<ref name="hrw-chn43081">{{cite web|url=http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/refworld/rwmain?page=search&docid=42df60bb11&skip=0&query=CHN43081.E|title=Responses To Information Requests "CHN43081.E"|author=Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada|publisher=UNHCR|accessdate=2013-02-24|quote=In a 23 November 2004 telephone interview with the Research Directorate, the senior researcher on China for HRW asserted that it would not have been possible for independent organisations to conduct an independent investigation of the incident. According to the senior researcher, the incident was among one of the most difficult stories for reporters in Beijing at the time to report on because of a lack of information and difficulties in ascertaining the extent of control of the information|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009082902/http://www.unhcr.org/cgi-bin/texis/vtx/refworld/rwmain?page=search&docid=42df60bb11&skip=0&query=CHN43081.E|archive-date=2012-10-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此該事件出現許多揣度與臆测，包括幕後主導者其實為中国政府<ref name="schechter1">{{Cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/Falun-Gongs-Challenge-China-Spiritual/dp/B007R949UO |title=Falun Gong's Challenge to China - A report by Danny Schechter |access-date=2013-03-03 |archive-date=2013-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130913102105/http://www.amazon.com/Falun-Gongs-Challenge-China-Spiritual/dp/B007R949UO |dead-url=no }}</ref>；也有人認為是個真實的抗議事件<ref>[http://www.hum.leidenuniv.nl/chinees/organisatie/medewerkers-alfabetisch/haarbjter.html Barend ter Haar] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hum.leidenuniv.nl/chinees/organisatie/medewerkers-alfabetisch/haarbjter.html |date=20091003100854 }}, Chair of Chinese History at Leiden University (Sinological Institute)[2013-02-24]</ref>；有人認為這是法輪功的新學員或者是不守教誨的學員所為<ref name="ownbyfalungong218">{{cite book |first=David |last=Ownby |title=Falun Gong and the future of China |url=https://archive.org/details/falungongfutureo2008ownb |publisher= Oxford University Press|year=2008|page=P.218|language=en|isbn=0-19-532905-8}}</ref>等等。美國獨立製片人與專欄作家[[丹尼·謝克特|丹尼·謝克特]]認為，此事件的報道始終缺乏官方以外的說法，判断中共吸取2000年除夕国际媒体关注法轮功学员在天安门广场抗议的教训，而策划了2001年除夕这场表演。<ref name="schechter1"/>。中華民國[[立法院|立法院]]2004年要求中共停止所谓鎮壓的決議說明文，指中共執政當局「發動全國宣傳機器，全面抹黑、污衊[[李洪志|李洪志]]先生，故外界亦一再質疑，大陸當局一手炮製[[天安門自焚事件|天安門自焚案]]等事件，意圖挑起一般人民對法輪功的仇恨。」<ref name=LY/>

中国政府在之后随即通过加大宣传力度来削弱公众对法轮功的亲和度。《[[時代雜誌|时代]]》杂志指出，许多中国人在以前并不觉得法轮功造成真正的威胁，認為當局的鎮壓與事實不符，并对当局对法轮功的镇压政策表示反对。但在自焚事件发生后，随着[[中国中央电视台|中央电视台]]等中国政府官方媒体集中报导该事件并集中批判法轮功后<ref name="breakingpoint">{{cite news |first=Matthew |last=Forney |url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,165163,00.html |title=The Breaking Point |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=2001-06-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013111614/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,165163,00.html |archivedate=2007-10-13 |accessdate=2007-11-02 }}</ref><ref name="Apple123"/>，民众开始对法轮功具有负面看法，各種批評法輪功的海報、傳單和視頻不斷被製作出來<ref name="oneway">{{Cite web|url=http://www.rickross.com/reference/fa_lun_gong/falun214.html|title=One-Way Trip to the End in Beijing|accessdate=2013-02-24|author=Philip P. Pan|date=2001-02-05|publisher=International Herald Tribune|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002214833/http://www.rickross.com/reference/fa_lun_gong/falun214.html|archivedate=2012-10-02|quote=|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="dangerous">{{cite book|first=Mickey|last=Spiegel|url=http://hrw.org/reports/2002/china/|title=Dangerous Meditation: China's Campaign Against Falungong|publisher=Human Rights Watch|year=2002|isbn=1-56432-270-X|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929164327/http://hrw.org/reports/2002/china/|archivedate=2007-09-29}}</ref><ref name="chrandra">{{cite journal|first=Chrandra D.|last=Smith|url=http://org.law.rutgers.edu/publications/law-religion/new_devs/RJLR_ND_66.pdf|format=PDF|title=Chinese Persecution of Falun Gong|publisher=Rutgers School of Law|journal=Rutgers Journal of Law and Religion|date=October 2004|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090327075424/http://org.law.rutgers.edu/publications/law-religion/new_devs/RJLR_ND_66.pdf|archivedate=2009-03-27}}</ref>。CNN指出，政府在此次事件中的宣传措施，和以往的政治运动，诸如[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]和[[文化大革命|文化大革命]]等非常相像<ref name="tense">{{Cite web|url=http://archives.cnn.com/2001/WORLD/asiapcf/east/01/24/asia.falun.03/|title=Tiananmen tense after fiery protests|accessdate=2013-02-24|date=2001-01-24|publisher=CNN|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222110517/http://archives.cnn.com/2001/WORLD/asiapcf/east/01/24/asia.falun.03/|archivedate=2007-02-22|quote=|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》形容中共「用電視、報紙等媒體圖像轟炸」，《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》指當局藉此事件「系統地暴力鎮壓」法輪功<ref name="Apple123"/>。后来，随着公众支持和舆论导向远离法轮功，外国声称中国当局也使用更加暴力的手段对待法轮功学员，例如酷刑<ref name="breaking">{{cite news|author=Philip Pan and John Pomfret|title=Torture is Breaking Falun Gong|newspaper= Washington Post|date= 2001-08-05|URL=https://archive.is/xVexH|accessdate=2013-02-24|language=en}}</ref> 。[[自由之家|自由之家]]声稱事件加強中共對國內異教和異見的打壓，涉案組織人士遭更严厉监禁和酷刑，在拘押期间死亡数字上升。<ref name=Freedomhouse>Sarah Cook, Sarah (4 November 2013) [http://www.freedomhouse.org/blog/be-skeptical-official-story-tiananmen-car-crash "Be Skeptical of the Official Story on the Tiananmen Car Crash"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.freedomhouse.org/blog/be-skeptical-official-story-tiananmen-car-crash |date=20140503002409 }} Freedom House.</ref>

==背景==
[[Image:April25Zhognanhai.jpg|thumb]]附近依法上訪。此后不久，在全国范围内针对法轮功的打压正式开始了。]]
{{See also|法輪功}}

法輪功又被稱為法輪大法，法輪功方面声稱，其為一種結合靜功與動功的健身[[氣功|氣功]]，同時又包含[[佛家|佛家]]與[[道家|道家]]等傳統思想；該功法於1992年春天由李洪志在中國東北吉林省傳出，在1990年代後期，吸引了上億人练功<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1999/04/27/world/in-beijing-a-roar-of-silent-protesters.html|title=In Beijing: A Roar of Silent Protesters|author=SETH FAISON|date=1999-04-27|publisher=''New York Times''|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140118211032/http://www.nytimes.com/1999/04/27/world/in-beijing-a-roar-of-silent-protesters.html|archivedate=2014-01-18}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1999/04/27/world/notoriety-now-for-movement-s-leader.html|title=Notoriety Now for Movement's Leader|author=JOSEPH KAHN|date=1999-04-27|publisher=''New York Times''|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105104339/http://www.nytimes.com/1999/04/27/world/notoriety-now-for-movement-s-leader.html|archivedate=2012-11-05}}</ref><ref name="Chang4">{{cite book|last=Chang|first=Maria Hsia|title=Falun Gong – The End of Days|url=https://archive.org/details/falungong00mari|publisher=Yale University Press|year=2004|page=page.4|isbn=978-0-300-10227-7}}</ref><ref name="ownby">{{cite book |first=Ownby |last=David |title=Falun Gong and the future of China |publisher= Oxford University Press|year=2008|page=|language= en|isbn=0-19-532905-8}}</ref>。法輪功在一開始得到中国政府官方的支持與認可<ref name="ownbyfalungong218"/>，但在1990年代中期，中国政府試圖箝制氣功的影響力，對國內的各種氣功團體訂定更加嚴格的規定<ref name="ownbyfalungong218"/><ref name="Palmer">{{cite book |first=David |last=Palmer |title=Qigong Fever: Body, Science, and Utopia in China|url=https://archive.org/details/qigongfeverbodys0000palm |publisher= Columbia University Press|year=2007|page=|language=en|isbn=978-0231140669}}</ref>。1996年開始，法輪功受到中共執政當局的國安機構越來越多的批評與監督<ref name="Tong">{{cite book|first=James |last=Tong |title=Revenge of the Forbidden City: The Suppression of the Falungong in China, 1999-2005|publisher= Oxford University Press|year=2009|page=|language= en|isbn= 0195377281}}</ref>。

1999年4月25日，上萬名的法輪功學員前往[[中共中央|中共中央]]、中国国务院所在地[[中南海|中南海]]依法向政府[[上訪|上訪]]表達訴求，要求合理的對待<ref name="Tong"/><ref name="Fuyou">{{Cite web|url=http://www.david-kilgour.com/2009/Jul_05_2009_04.php|title=An Occurrence on Fuyou Street|author=Ethan Gutmann|date=2009-07-13|publisher=National Review|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604114413/http://www.david-kilgour.com/2009/Jul_05_2009_04.php|archivedate=2013-06-04}}</ref>。传言称當天晚上，时任[[中共中央總書記|中共中央總書記]][[江澤民|江澤民]]決定剷除法輪功；在江澤民的指示下，1999年6月7日中共中央為此事成立了專門的領導小組<ref name="Jamestown">{{Cite web|url=http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=38411&cHash=2dff246d80ffd78112de97e280ce9725|title=The 610 Office: Policing the Chinese Spirit|author=Sarah Cook, Leeshai Lemish|date=2011-09-16|publisher=China Brief,Volume 11 Issue 17|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926215246/http://www.jamestown.org/programs/chinabrief/single/?chash%3D2dff246d80ffd78112de97e280ce9725%26tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D%3D38411|archivedate=2011-09-26}}</ref>。此組織名為「[[610辦公室|610辦公室]]」，其專門協調政府官方媒體的反法輪功工作，並影響其它黨與國家的機構，例如法院和國安機構<ref name="Tong"/><ref name="Jamestown"/>。1999年7月19日，中共中央下達文件，禁止共产党员修煉法輪功；翌日，數百名法輪功學員遭到公安逮捕拘留<ref name="Tong"/><ref name="Amnesty">{{Cite web|url=https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:JSlU_AqX6nYJ:www.amnesty.org/en/library/asset/ASA17/011/2000/en/77562be8-df70-11dd-acaa-7d9091d4638f/asa170112000en.pdf+&hl=zh-TW&gl=tw&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESgIIfQFSF2nCIrQpLOPARwdplWDFRG1IboHRqW2HmKhBJQC5ZWEw7vYyQwB8X6bCJ46fyYSlLDGcTtvHxxX-MnV0bsx-PKFhAOLsObDTv9lSkeo2JQfs18wAF7iAnXiBdd9kFje&sig=AHIEtbREeV1y8x5FHkqHSmgoIjLiztegGg|title=China: The crackdown on Falun Gong and other so-called "heretical organization"|author=Amnesty International|date=2000-03-23|publisher=|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726015719/https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache%3AJSlU_AqX6nYJ%3Awww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flibrary%2Fasset%2FASA17%2F011%2F2000%2Fen%2F77562be8-df70-11dd-acaa-7d9091d4638f%2Fasa170112000en.pdf+&hl=zh-TW&gl=tw&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESgIIfQFSF2nCIrQpLOPARwdplWDFRG1IboHRqW2HmKhBJQC5ZWEw7vYyQwB8X6bCJ46fyYSlLDGcTtvHxxX-MnV0bsx-PKFhAOLsObDTv9lSkeo2JQfs18wAF7iAnXiBdd9kFje&sig=AHIEtbREeV1y8x5FHkqHSmgoIjLiztegGg|archive-date=2014-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]描述上述行動為：「透過『大規模的宣傳活動』，將法輪功形容為迷信而危險的，且不符合中国共产党的思想意識，進而使鎮壓合理化。」<ref name="Amnesty"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://faluninfo.net/article/565/-i-Wall-Street-Journal-i-Death-Trap-How-One-Chinese-City-Resorted-to-Atrocities-To-Control-Falun-Dafa/|title=Death Trap - How One Chinese City Resorted to Atrocities To Control Falun Dafa|author=Ian Johnson|date=2000-12-26|publisher=Wall Street Journal|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714181047/http://faluninfo.net/article/565/-i-Wall-Street-Journal-i-Death-Trap-How-One-Chinese-City-Resorted-to-Atrocities-To-Control-Falun-Dafa/|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

以江泽民为首的中共執政當局决定鎮壓法轮功後，北京天安門廣場成為法輪功學員表達抗議訴求的地方之一，法輪功學員通常以標語旗幟或靜坐等和平方式進行抗議<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/26/world/falun-gong-holds-protests-on-anniversary-of-big-sit-in.html|title=Falun Gong Holds Protests On Anniversary of Big Sit-In|author=Elisabeth Rosenthal|date=2001-04-26|publisher=''New York Times''|language=en|accessdate=2013-02-26|quote=|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714164825/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/26/world/falun-gong-holds-protests-on-anniversary-of-big-sit-in.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>。据美國《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》報導，到2000年4月25日為止，中国有超過3萬名的法輪功學員遭到逮捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pulitzer.org/archives/6464 |title=Defiant Falun Dafa Members Converge on Tiananmen |first=Ian |last=Johnson |date=2000-04-25 |work=The Wall Street Journal |language=en |publisher=Pulitzer.org |page=page A21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091229022658/http://www.pulitzer.org/archives/6464 |archivedate=2009-12-29 |access-date=2013-03-03 }}</ref>；2001年1月1日，有700名法輪功學員在天安門廣場的抗議活動中遭到逮捕<ref name="Perry">{{cite book |first=Elizabeth J.|last=Selden|coauthor=Perry, Mark |title=Chinese Society: Change, Conflict and Resistance|publisher=Routledge |year=2003 |language=en |isbn=041530170X}}</ref>。

2001年元月22日[[法新社|法新社]]以『中共因镇压法轮功失败而惊恐』为题，报导中共承认无法阻止每天数百法轮功成员在[[天安门广场|天安门广场]]和平抗议。报导提及，在18个月来的镇压中，尽管法轮功学员遭受各式各样的攻击，有 50,000人被拘留，但未屈服于压力，而是变得更坚定。并提及中共领导层对江泽民的镇压有很大分歧，许多领导人表态反对镇压。报导援引香港中文大学的刘苏凯（音译）教授的话： “江应为下令镇压负主要责任，镇压运动毫无结果，江将政府逼入死角。事后看来，镇压非常鲁莽和轻率，尤其是在中国正努力在世界上重塑形象的时候。江骑虎难下。这涉及到它个人权力的问题。它担心如果给他们一点呼吸的空间，他就会被党内看做软弱，而无法保持最高领导地位。 ” <ref>{{cite web|title=China Spooked by Failure to Crush Falungong|first=|last=|date=2000-01-22 |work=AFP|language=en|publisher= |page=}}{{quote| China's leadership is increasingly alarmed and divided by the failure of its campaign to destroy the Falungong as it braces for new protests on the eve of the Spring Festival. For 18 months the spiritual movement has weathered an all-out assault, and despite the violent suppression of peaceful protests it still gathers hundreds of followers in Beijing's Tiananmen Square to mark key dates. In a surprising admission of failure, China said earlier this month it had been unable to prevent hundreds of Falungong members protesting daily in the square. There is a major split within the senior leadership. There are many leaders who are voicing disagreement with the crackdown."Jiang bears the major responsibility for ordering the crackdown," said Professor Lau Siu-kai of the Chinese University in Hong Kong. "The move has not borne fruit and Jiang has pushed the government into a corner. With hindsight it looks rash and over-confident, particularly as China is trying to rebuild its image in the world," he said. Factions in government believe the violent suppression of protests are hurting China's image just as it battles to overcome the damaging legacy of the military's crushing of the 1989 pro-democracy movement. Frank Lu says the crackdown does not have strong support within the leadership."Jiang can't back down. It involves his power. He's afraid if he gives them a little breathing space, he'll look weak in front of the party and not strong enough to keep being a top leader," he said.}}</ref>

==事件經過==
<div class="toccolours" style="float: right; margin-left: 2em; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 85%; background:#fffffa; color:black; width:25em; max-width: 35%; padding: 1em 1.5em 1.5em">

'''纪录片《''伪火''》中列举出的所谓疑点<ref name="FalseFire">{{cite web | url=http://www.falsefire.com/ | title=Analysis and Insights about the "self-Immolation" | publisher=falsefire.com New Tang Dynasty Television | accessdate=2014-12-12 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217101557/http://falsefire.com/ | archivedate=2014-12-17 }}</ref>'''
<br/>
一部由法轮功学员参与的新唐人电视台拍摄的纪录片《伪火》<ref>Susan V. Lawrence, "Falun Gong Adds Media Weapons in Struggle With China's Rulers", ''The Wall Street Journal''. (Eastern edition), 14 April 2004. pg. B.2I</ref>指出了一些在事件中所谓和中国官方描述不一样的地方，包括：<ref name="upholdjustice.org">[http://www.upholdjustice.org/English.2/S_I_second_report.htm "Second Investigation Report on the 'Tiananmen Square Self-Immolation Incident.'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.upholdjustice.org/English.2/S_I_second_report.htm |date=20071119085438 }}, World Organization to Investigate the Persecution of Falun Gong (WOIPFalun Gong), August 2003. Retrieved 6 February 2007</ref><ref name=hrw-chn43081/>

*刘春玲在自焚时似乎被一不明身份的男子用钝器对头予以重击。因此纪录片认为，刘并非自焚身亡，而是因为头部受到严重击打死亡。
*从央视所提供的监视录像来看，王进东似乎穿戴着防火衣和面具；片方质疑为何他的头发和他们身上装汽油的塑胶瓶并未被烧着。
*警方通常不会携带灭火器进行值班。录像显示，自焚事件当天，只有两辆警车在现场，从最近的建筑物到事发地点最快也得有10分钟路程。然而，在自焚开始到火焰被扑灭，只花了不到一分钟的时间。
*在天安门广场的监控摄像头通常是固定的，但是事件当天却能清楚地拍摄到摄像头本不能拍摄到的地方。
*王进东在自焚时喊出的口号，手的位置和坐姿，均不是法轮大法在教义中所教导的。
*当时的自焚重伤者刘思影被送到积水潭医院后，按理应该被送入重症监护室（无菌室）予以隔离治療。但是中国官方媒体中央电视台所播出的采访片段中显示，记者不经任何消毒和隔离便近距离采访刘思影。
*积水潭医院方面表示在送院当天进行了气管切割手术，但是刘思影却能在短时间内便能说话甚至唱歌。
</div>

[[2001年|2001年]]1月23日，這天同時也是[[中國|中國]]傳統節日中的除夕，當時有5人在天安門廣場自焚，另外還有2人也要進行自焚行為，但未點燃汽油。<ref name="dangerous"/><ref name="missions">{{cite web|url=http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/200101/31/eng20010131_61313.html|title=Suicidal Blaze, Another Crime of Falun Gong Cult|publisher=[[新华社|新华社]]|language=en|date=2001-01-31|accessdate=2013-02-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022220405/http://english.peopledaily.com.cn/200101/31/eng20010131_61313.html|archivedate=2012-10-22}}</ref>。當時属于美國[[有線電視新聞網|有線電視新聞網]]（CNN）的一个團隊正在現場準備拍攝當天可能會發生的法輪功抗議活動<ref name="mulls">{{cite news |first=Philip |last=Pan |work=The Washington Post |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn/A44880-2001Feb8?language=printer |title=China Mulls Murder Charges for Foreign Journalists |date=2001-02-08|language=en|publisher=|accessdate= 2013-02-26}}</ref>，他們看到有一名男子走到位於廣場中心的[[人民英雄紀念碑|人民英雄紀念碑]]的東北方，並坐了下來<ref name="tense"/>，接著他把[[汽油|汽油]]澆在身上，然後點火<ref name="tense"/>。

現場的公安立刻趕到男子所在處，並試圖撲滅火勢<ref name="tense"/>。不久之後，另外4個人也相繼點火，4人當中有一位男子立刻被公安架走<ref name="tense"/>。根據美國有線電視新聞網CNN的報道，當時5人當中至少有2名男性，但其中沒有小孩。但中国政府官方的報導稱自焚的5人是1名男性、4名女性，包括1名12歲的小女孩。美國有線電視新聞網團隊對此事件進行拍攝，直到[[武警|武警]]介入並拘留他們<ref name="tense"/>。當局隨後撲滅了4人身上的火勢<ref name="tense"/>，一輛警車進入，將傷勢嚴重的那名男性載走；大約25分鐘後，一輛救護車到達現場，將其餘4人載走<ref name="tense"/>。天安門廣場遭到全面封鎖<ref>Mickey Spiegel, {{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/?id=klyC1eH97pQC&pg=PA33&dq=%22China+responded+to+the+even+unusually+quickly,+completely+shutting+down+Tiananment+Square%22&q= |title=DANGEROUS MEDITATION China's Campaign Against Falungong, page 33|publisher=Human Rights Watch, 2002, ISBN 978-1-56432-270-8 |accessdate=2013-02-26 |isbn=978-1-56432-269-2 |date=2002-01|language=en }}</ref>。CNN报导，在事件发生之后的隔天即中國新年，公安對廣場進行嚴密監控，嚴加防備法輪功學員展開橫幅或旗幟，并在昨天事件发生处準備了多个滅火器。<ref name="tense"/>。

自焚的5人當中，劉春玲當場死亡；而她12歲的女兒劉思影，在當年3月，也就是住院2個月後，在北京醫院過世<ref name="Siying">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/1228576.stm |title=  Tiananmen 'suicide' girl dies  |accessdate=2013-02-26 |language=en| date=2001-03-18| work=BBC News}}</ref>。

